  "text": "As mentioned earlier, in [CITATION_1] there are examples of matrices M with NP-complete M -partition problems for chordal graphs. The matrices constructed in [CITATION_2] have a fairly large size, say, in the neighbourhood of thirty rows and columns; we do not know what is the smallest size of a matrix M with an NP-complete M -partition problem.",
